{"tid":842631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做人窮慣左真係好恐怖","createTime":"2018-09-30T13:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T13:45:56.000Z","uid":206210,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e642ec1d47990adaeae761da04d1f028c765b3","tid":842631,"uid":206210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"其實我都明白人一出世係無得選擇屋企人<br />\n而我屋企人都對我好好<br />\n我都好愛我屋企人<br />\n<br />\n但唯一覺得好辛苦係<br />\n大家的思想同目標都唔係同一個方向<br />\n姐係作為一個公屋妹 <br />\n見到居屋52折就點都想試下抽唔抽得中 <br />\n但佢地就寧願每個月 <br />\n飲多倆餐茶 去多次短旅行 舒服咁生活<br />\n都好過壓幾千出黎供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窮慣左真係好恐怖 <br />\n有多一日假 飲多餐茶已經好滿足<br />\n邊得閒去想其他野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4672a9de7cf7f8901749a5cb8ca831f3a93d2e2a","tid":842631,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:17:42.000Z","msg":"點解一定要買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b22b53c39f4077628fd5e21fff6f63729443c46","tid":842631,"uid":206210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4672a9de7cf7f8901749a5cb8ca831f3a93d2e2a","tid":842631,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:17:42.000Z","msg":"點解一定要買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:20:23.000Z","msg":"因為住公屋遲早都會被人收番間屋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fd5a96628d0b537c0976114bfd763921ff17d0","tid":842631,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b22b53c39f4077628fd5e21fff6f63729443c46","tid":842631,"uid":206210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4672a9de7cf7f8901749a5cb8ca831f3a93d2e2a","tid":842631,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTim